Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:03.70,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的名字是觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:05.12,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神尾觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:08.13,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也得給你取個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:11.89,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}放學時碰到的那個哥哥簡直是鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:14.45,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在誰還會看那種人偶戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.64,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:18.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對了  小空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.30,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就叫你小空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:23.94,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:27.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我平時仰望天空的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.48,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.42,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}似乎不是病了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:25.94,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.37,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣就好像是朋友一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.01,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夕陽真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:36.62,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也真想像那樣和人一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.42,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個黑玩意是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跟回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像還很小  飛不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這東西居然也跟你這麼親熱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我給它取了個名字  叫小空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想跟它一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:14.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇…  這麼快就拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想要寵物的話就去找貓狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把這種東西放在家裏也太鬱悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:26.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來  問候一下媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}眼睛--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:30.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽非常生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今晚就偷偷讓你住在我房裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明天一起向媽媽道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明天開始就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:50.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我今年想試著邀請一下同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  大家會陪我玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:54.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}練習一下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:59.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}暑假能和我一起玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  因為我要補習所以只有下午有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:06.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們可以去海邊游泳  可以打牌  可以放煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還可以一起寫作業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我只要照抄就可以了  很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}中午前會回來的  先隨便玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要跑得太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊  是烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的呢  黑乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真討厭  看著好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}挺可愛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊!  飛過來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你給我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？ 是烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是從哪裏來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:19.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不會欺負你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這還不能解開的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}長大後再解開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就可以使用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}路上有車  要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:41.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶吶  去不去海邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:48.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去  去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我今年買的泳裝很暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不可以哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}忍耐  忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個夏天我也要一個人過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒能約到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為大家都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我與一般人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過我會一個人做高興的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自由課題就畫繪畫日記了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把高興的事情全都畫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  所以不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是昨天那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:41.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我還是不想孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:46.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不想孤零零的度過漫長的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:50.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我跟他打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果是個好人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就試著約他一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  微笑微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裝得自然一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拉麵套餐--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:25.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼又跑出來一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:31.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又跑出一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又跑出一個啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}害我連說了三遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:39.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道我受了多大打擊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:42.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跟你說的不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}膽子倒是不小  這一點倒不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  往人是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧  就留下你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:53.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:53.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}當然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是叫國崎往人來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那傢伙好像和觀鈴很合得來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴不會又發作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:09.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}或許  那傢伙可以和觀鈴成為朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子因為那個病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以一直沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看上去也不像壞傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就在他身上賭賭看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:23.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有別的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剩下的都是小號的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:31.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:34.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人和媽媽有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:36.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也要補習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你來看家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都已經買好了  怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在這幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:18.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正好  陪我走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這裏馬上就有夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從那時算來已經是第十次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在記得依然很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:39.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子坐在賣小雞的地方一直說個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎哦  嘎哦的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:45.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她以為小雞長大了就會變成恐龍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:49.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在廟會上買的小雞怎麼可能養大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:53.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就拉起她的手打算帶她回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:10:00.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}早就告訴過她不可以給別人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:04.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但那時她卻一直看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:08.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好意思地說「我想要這個」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:12.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴並不是在父母的恩愛下出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:17.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是連婚都沒結的兩個人在各種爭吵中生下的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:21.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}姐姐留下孩子和男人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:25.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}男人便把這孩子硬塞給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是受了不少累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:37.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直都是相信那個男人很快就會來把她帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:42.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  我和那孩子生活了這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她總是慌慌張張毛手毛腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但又總是在笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到她  我也就想笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:58.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我畢竟不是她的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}或許那個男人今天就會帶走她也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:08.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那樣的話  我就不得不重新一個人過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我只能為了分別時不太凄慘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:16.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而維持自己的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:21.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以從來沒有給她買過生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每年都是裝作忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今年也猶豫了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}事到如今  還怎麼變成真正的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:43.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我確實曾經見過那個人  也見過這片風景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:48.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是  是什麼時候  在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我怎麼也想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:59.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  知了又從天窗進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  醬油瓶倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:06.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  色拉油灑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人的咸肉雞蛋  出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人  好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:15.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:16.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:17.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吃起來不像知了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:24.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎  嘎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  去哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}古怪的烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:40.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}願彩香姐姐的病能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:44.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽  真的有神嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}當然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:51.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神一直在看著彩香和舞香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:53.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一定會實現願望的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽  這是神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人在走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像還是新的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}放在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這裏是神的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:16.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不逃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:33.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:37.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有家的話  就一起去車站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:43.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和小滿一定會成為好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:46.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還有很多吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}超級幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:55.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎  你有回去的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}總有一天會靠著那翅膀飛起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:10.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你每次發作我都會被叫到學校去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:14.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和那吃白飯的在一起的時候沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還以為你治好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:17.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  對不起添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽生氣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:37.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  她聽說後很快就來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每次都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人在等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}會擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得盡量裝得自然一些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就好像忘了約定一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:55.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想讓往人把我當成普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:13.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:14.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小空  媽媽說往人搬出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我還想跟他在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:30.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  他說會接送我到學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  要忍耐才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今後也可以每天見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:46.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最近後背有時會痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:56.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼要收養觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:59.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你害得她沒法向你撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自覺一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:03.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對她來說  你是唯一的親人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說得還真難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用你說我也早就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不能總是這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}生日也不送禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我怕不知什麼時候就會失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:23.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要讓她成為我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}直接到橘的家裏去談判
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對  一個人悠然地去作溫泉之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你到底在想什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:40.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她…  觀鈴怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}繼續待在這裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們倆都沒救的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我要從你身邊逃開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那麼  沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒辦法的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:01.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與往人一起度過的暑假很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:02.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也是
